{"tid":2120921,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國放寬 BNO 港人居留　中國駐英使館︰嚴重干涉內政，將有力回應","createTime":"2020-07-23T03:55:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T05:25:50.000Z","uid":36494,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"cb2aa3f53be1be15bd9dde9afbb161a75ca0e3b6","tid":2120921,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T03:55:24.000Z","msg":"英國周三 (22/7) 公布容許擁有可領英國國民海外護照 (BNO) 身份的港人，明年 1 月起的申請居留及入籍安排。申請人可最長一次過居留 5 年，期間允許在當地工作或讀書，以及攜同家屬前往英國，居留滿 6 年可申請入籍。<br />\n<br />\n中國駐英使館發言人今日批評，英方不顧中方強烈反對和一再交涉，為有關人員在英居留和入籍提供路徑，嚴重違背自身承諾，嚴重干涉中國內政，嚴重違反國際法和國際關系基本准則，對此表示強烈不滿和堅決反對，並揚言「將做出有力回應」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E6%94%BE%E5%AF%AC-bno-%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%B1%85%E7%95%99-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%A7%90%E8%8B%B1%E4%BD%BF%E9%A4%A8-%E5%9A%B4%E9%87%8D%E5%B9%B2%E6%B6%89%E5%85%A7%E6%94%BF-%E5%B0%87%E6%9C%89%E5%8A%9B%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2594%25BE%25E5%25AF%25AC-bno-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25B1%2585%25E7%2595%2599-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%25A7%2590%25E8%258B%25B1%25E4%25BD%25BF%25E9%25A4%25A8-%25E5%259A%25B4%25E9%2587%258D%25E5%25B9%25B2%25E6%25B6%2589%25E5%2585%25A7%25E6%2594%25BF-%25E5%25B0%2587%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%258A%259B%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2587%2589%2F&d=DosFxDX7yTzXLN9Gri3QgFpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=38c5dde8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2594%25BE%25E5%25AF%25AC-bno-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25B1%2585%25E7%2595%2599-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%25A7%2590%25E8%258B%25B1%25E4%25BD%25BF%25E9%25A4%25A8-%25E5%259A%25B4%25E9%2587%258D%25E5%25B9%25B2%25E6%25B6%2589%25E5%2585%25A7%25E6%2594%25BF-%25E5%25B0%2587%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%258A%259B%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2587%2589%2F&h=afb5de56\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\